title: I LOVE LISTS
description: I LOVE LISTS Imagine seeing one of these cars IRL. On the to do list: quick strawberry cake Also this strawberry matcha latte looks so good! Surreal landscapes lit by drones. World Press photo contest winners. Let’s look at Diana Ross’ stage outfits! Time travel: old American architecture Advice from someone who used to work a deli counter. Do you know about the fish doorbell? Is soft-serve just melted ice cream? What did Hubble see on your birthday? Some tricks to get rid of weeds in your garden. Don’t grocery shop hungry. Jumpsuit love: one / two / three / four That’s a lot of paper moths & butterflies. What a time to be alive. Speaking of, ChatGPT got an image upgrade. Things to ask yourself before buying a home. My favorite cleaning supplies! I started a Shutterbean Meal Prep board on my Pinterest. Let’s CONNECT! Join me TOMORROW- Saturday, March 29th, from 12- 1ish PM PST for a special Handwriting Club Show & Tell—a special ZOOM hangout for paid subscribers. We’ll be gathering to: Share and work on our Spring Bucket List/Bingo – Set intentions for the new season. Review and complete our March pages – A final reflection before we work on April! Wrap up our Winter Bucket List/Bingo – Winter is officially done, so let’s take some time to celebrate what we accomplished. More information can be found here!
